## AUDIT_FAIL

**Reason**: The agent did not implement the feature despite claiming it was "fully achieved." The permission restrictions on Edit/Write/Bash tools prevented actual implementation. The agent should have clearly reported this blocker instead of concluding success. No code changes are present in the repository to support the claimed feature completion.

**What needs to happen next**: 
1. Verify permissions allow Edit/Write/Bash tool use
2. Restart work with explicit focus on implementing shell completions in `sw-init.sh`
3. Add corresponding tests to `sw-init-test.sh`
4. Avoid distraction from the unrelated `sw-hygiene.sh` failure (file a separate issue if needed)
